Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Talibon Provincial Hospital in the Municipality of Talibon, Province of Bohol, to Congressman Maximino Garcia Memorial Hospital
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 714
An Act Changing the Name of the Talibon Provincial Hospital in the Municipality of Talibon, Province of Bohol, to Congressman Maximino Garcia Memorial Hospital
Section 1. The name of the Talibon Provincial Hospital in the Municipality of Talibon, Province of Bohol, is changed to Congressman Maximino Garcia Memorial Hospital.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
